data.description: Buyer Financing Fell Through! BACK ON MARKET!  Welcome to the Turn-Key Ready Townhome located at 9523 Mary Geneva Lane! This Luxurious Brick Front Townhouse is Full of Upgrades! Introducing an exquisite opportunity to own a piece of modern luxury in the highly sought-after Ballard Green neighborhood of Owings Mills . This six-year-old gem is sure to impress. Step into this well-cared-for 3 Bedroom, 2 Full and 2 Half Bathrooms abode that generously offers over 2,100 SQ FT of comfortable living space spread across three levels. Each of the three well-appointed levels offers 9 foot ceilings and oversized windows- ensuring a plethora of natural light radiating throughout the home. There is a bath on every level. The home features a luxurious chef's kitchen with granite countertops and energy efficient stainless steel appliances making mealtime a breeze. The open floor plan allows easy access to the main floor living room, dining room and eat-in kitchen. The chief’s kitchen has everything you could hope for including a six person breakfast bar, an upgraded stainless steel appliance package, a pantry, maintenance-free deck access and best of all, it overlooks the openly designed main living area. Upstairs you will find a spacious master bedroom, including an en-suite bathroom (w/standing glass shower and dual sinks), a walk-in closet, and full size front loading washer and dryer. The other two bedrooms are generous in size and closet space. To make life easier, throw the clothes in the bedroom level laundry and forget about it for the night. Your convenience is valued, and this home ensures it with a one-car garage and an accommodating driveway, making parking a hassle-free affair. Embrace community living with delightful amenities including a Clubhouse equipped with a pool, fitness center and kitchen/entertaining space that can be reserved for your events. Ideally situated, this residence offers easy access to a range of lifestyle essentials including shopping centers, dining options, and parks for leisurely strolls. Its central location offers easy access to 95, 695 and 795. This is your chance to embrace a modern lifestyle while enjoying the tranquility of a welcoming community. This gem will not last so schedule a private tour today!
